# Goal: probe a block with a push/pull test (block_pose is the estimated pose in the tower)
uint32 block_index
geometry_msgs/PoseStamped block_pose
---
# Result: outcome (score is a simple numeric metric; interpretation is task-specific)
bool success
string message
uint8 error_code
float32 score
---
# Feedback: progress
string current_stage
float32 progress_pct
